; Regression test for issue #2335:
; getquote errors are not reported
;
; When the getquote script fails (non-zero exit) or returns no usable
; price data, a warning should be emitted to stderr so the user is
; informed rather than silently receiving no price update.

2024/01/15 Buy Stock
    Assets:Brokerage        10 BADQUOTE
    Assets:Checking        $-1000.00

; BADQUOTE causes mock-getquote.sh to exit 1 -- a warning must appear
test bal --market --download --getquote $sourcepath/test/scripts/mock-getquote.sh -> 0
                   0  Assets
            $1000.00    Brokerage
           $-1000.00    Checking
--------------------
                   0
__ERROR__
Warning: Price quote script failed for commodity 'BADQUOTE'
end test
